    <item>
      <title>美国经济前景恶化，全球债券抹去今年的损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/global-bonds-erase-this-year-s-loss-as-us-economic-outlook-sours</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国经济前景的担忧迅速恶化，刺激了对固定收益资产的需求，全球债券已经抹去了今年的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/global-bonds-erase-this-year-s-loss-as-us-economic-outlook-sours</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:27:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>彭博社观点：日本准备好迎接“充满兴趣的世界”了吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/bloomberg-opinion-is-japan-ready-for-a-world-with-interest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本，整整一代人都是在接近零利率的环境中长大的，但现在他们正准备迎接银行存款年化收益率可能达到 0.1% 的时代。彭博社观点专栏作家 Gearoid Reidy 一直在关注日本的“美丽新世界”，他在彭博电视台发表了讲话。他的观点是他自己的。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/bloomberg-opinion-is-japan-ready-for-a-world-with-interest</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:25:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股价下跌令投资者震惊，黄金也遭遇抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/gold-gets-dragged-into-selloff-as-share-slide-jolts-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受全球股市疲软拖累，金价在亚洲早盘一度下跌 1.2%，抵消了对中东紧张局势加剧的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/gold-gets-dragged-into-selloff-as-share-slide-jolts-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:07:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球股市暴跌加剧，推动债券上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，全球股市抛售加剧，人们越来越担心美联储在支持美国经济放缓的政策方面落后于形势，投资者纷纷转向债券避险。日本股市连续第三天暴跌，因为交易员认为国内利率将进一步上调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本东证指数和日经指数较 7 月高点下跌 20%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japan-s-stock-rout-enters-third-day-with-nikkei-in-bear-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于日元升值、货币政策收紧以及美国经济前景恶化导致投资者信心崩溃，日本股市基准指数较上个月创下的历史高点下跌了约 20%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japan-s-stock-rout-enters-third-day-with-nikkei-in-bear-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:18:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比索下跌、日元和人民币升值，套利交易平仓扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/global-carry-trade-unwind-extends-as-peso-sinks-yen-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一日元和人民币走高，而墨西哥比索的跌势延续，因交易员继续平仓新兴市场套利交易。]]></description>
